                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Sedulius Si<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">lanus? f(ilius)</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Seduli Maior<supplied reason="lost">is <expan><abbr>nep</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan>? <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>di Silani <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>erdos</ex></expan> Au<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex cert="low">usti</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/>arcum s<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>atuas idem M<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Im CIL sind zwei Lesungen überliefert; alternative Lesung: Z. 1: Q. SEDVLIVS SII; Z. 3: DIS MARIS AC; Z. 4: AC ARCVM / STATVAS IDEM / M D D; so auch bei Le Bohec.</p>
